    <scopecontent>
      <head>Scope and Content Information</head>
      <p>The collection consists of three untitled manuscript poems
         written by Faulkner on the end papers of a book 
         <title xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" xlink:type="simple" render="italic" xlink:href="">Poems</title>by Ralph Hodgson, together
         with the title page of the book and the half-title page
         containing Faulkner's signature and address.</p>
    </scopecontent>
